## purpose
Defines the architectural role of 0200090005 MARKET ACTIVITY ARCHITECTURE
as a bounded canonical structure.

## design_intent
This subject exists to make identity,
role,
activity,
boundary,
validation,
and failure meaning explicit
before later layers implement them.

## required_behavior
- identity meaning must remain explicit
- role meaning must remain explicit
- activity meaning must remain explicit
- boundary meaning must remain explicit
- validation meaning must remain explicit
- failure meaning must remain explicit

## canonical_rules
- projections must not overwrite truth
- hidden authority crossing is prohibited
- state transitions must remain reviewable
- ambiguity fails closed

## state_model
This subject distinguishes
registered state,
active state,
restricted state,
historical state,
and closed state.

## transition_rules
A transition must preserve identity,
boundary,
activity meaning,
and reviewability.

## actor_boundary
